# Keep the Netlify Functions source out of the Vercel static deploy.
# (Vercel builds functions from /api. The netlify/ tree stays in the repo so
#  the Netlify site keeps working as the one-week rollback fallback, but it
#  should not ship as static assets on Vercel.)
netlify/

# Internal working files, stale site snapshots, and source materials that must
# never be served publicly from ohiopride.org. The /api functions import from
# lib/, so lib/ is deliberately NOT ignored here.
Update/
OhioPride-Refocused/
oppr-fix/
patches/
ohiopride-pr-bundle 3/
docs/
scripts/
supabase/
assets/img/src/
*.md
*.sql
*.xlsx
